<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<font face="arial" style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi&nbsp;</span>{!Service__c.Contact_First_Name__c}<span style="font-size: 12pt;">​,&nbsp;</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Hope your week is going great! I wanted to follow up on the previous email, please note in order for <b>Bright MLS</b> to approve the IDX display on your website they require agents to submit an IDX request through their portal.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b>Follow these steps to submit IDX and VOW licensing requests to Bright:</b>&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">1. Log into <a href="http://brightmls.com/home">brightmls.com</a> and select Account &amp; Settings from the drop-down menu under your name.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">2. From the My Subscription tab, go to IDX and VOW Licensing Request. Note, if you have more than one subscription with Bright, you’ll be prompted to choose the appropriate ID and then continue.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">3. Next, please select that you would like an IDX website.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">4. In the Vendor Name field, please select Luxury Presence.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">5. In the Website URL field, enter your full personal/agent website address. Please be sure to include the URL address (www) along with the domain extension (.com, .org, .net).&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">6. Review your entry and when ready, click Submit.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">If you have any questions about the status of your request, please contact:</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">&nbsp;brokerauthorization@brightmls.com.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">After you complete these steps, please reach out to your managing broker to approve the request on their end, and then Luxury Presence will receive an email notification once the request has been processed!&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Lastly, if you do <b>not</b> have a Domain/URL finalized, no problem! Please wait until your next call with your Implementation Manager and they will be able to discuss URL options with you in detail. Let me know if you have any questions in the meantime. I'm here to help!</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Best Regards,</span></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>